nl.itc.RIMapper
Class ParseXML

java.lang.Object
  nl.itc.RIMapper.ParseXML

public class ParseXML
extends Object

Parses RIMapper XML files and returns handles to further process them into SVG output.
NOTE: this is the older way of configuring RIMapper instances (pre-WMS).
